### Roles API Manual Test Collection

@base = http://localhost:3000/api
@auth = Bearer {{token}}

### Crear rol
POST {{base}}/roles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth}}

{
  "name": "editor",
  "description": "Rol para edición de contenido"
}
###

### Listar roles
GET {{base}}/roles
Authorization: {{auth}}
###

### Obtener rol por id
GET {{base}}/roles/1
Authorization: {{auth}}
###

### Actualizar rol
PUT {{base}}/roles/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth}}

{
  "description": "Rol editor (actualizado)"
}
###

### Eliminar rol
DELETE {{base}}/roles/1
Authorization: {{auth}}
###

### Notas
# - Verificar códigos: 201 (create), 200 (list/get/update/delete), 400/409 en errores.
# - Requiere token con permisos de role.create/role.read/role.update/role.delete según endpoint.
